.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: blue, green, red, white, yellow
Nationality: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
Food: blueberry, zucchini, pepper, cabbage, radish
Cigar: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
Pet: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. Nationality:british == Color:red
2. Nationality:swedish == Pet:dog
3. Nationality:danish == Food:cabbage
4. Color:green is on the left of Color:white
5. Color:green == Food:zucchini
6. Cigar:pall-mall == Pet:bird
7. Color:yellow == Cigar:dunhill
8. Food:pepper is in the middle
9. Nationality:norwegian is on the far left
10. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Pet:cat
11. Pet:horses is on the left or right of Cigar:dunhill
12. Cigar:bluemaster == Food:blueberry
13. Nationality:german == Cigar:prince
14. Nationality:norwegian is on the left or right of Color:blue
15. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Food:radish

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     cat	|    horse	|     bird	|     fish	|      dog	|
| Food	|    radish	|     cabbage	|     pepper	|    zucchini	|      blueberry	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   bluemaster	|
